<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3145799" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="2"><ahelp hid=".">Inserts the page number into the current slide or page.</ahelp> If you want to add a page number to every slide, choose View - Master<switchinline select="appl"><caseinline select="IMPRESS"> - Slide Master
</caseinline></switchinline> and insert the page number field. To change the number format, choose <emph>Format - Page</emph> and then select a format from the list in the <emph>Layout Settings</emph> area.</paragraph>
